---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="CyberChallenge.IT - Training" description="CyberChallenge.IT: The premier Italian training initiative for cybersecurity professionals.">
  <main class="container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="glitch" data-text="CyberChallenge.IT">CyberChallenge.IT</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Formiamo la nuova generazione di Cyberdefender</p>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="/images/cyberchallenge2026.jpg" alt="CyberChallenge 2026" />
      </div>

      <div class="editions-grid">
        <section class="card edition-card">
          <h3>The Program</h3>
          <p>CyberChallenge.IT is the premier Italian training initiative designed to identify, attract, recruit, and place the next generation of cybersecurity professionals. It is a highly specialized program aimed at young, talented individuals between the ages of 16 and 24.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="card edition-card accent">
          <h3>Who Can Join?</h3>
          <p>You do not need to be a programming expert to participate. What you do need is passion, dedication, and a strong curiosity. We are looking for sharp logical reasoning, problem-solving skills, effective communication, and, above all, a strong desire to learn.</p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <section class="intro-section">
        <div class="text-block">
          <h2>National Recognition</h2>
          <p>Since 2020, CyberChallenge.IT has been officially recognized by the Italian Ministry of Education as a project for the "valorization of excellence." Through this initiative, the Ministry identifies and rewards the high-level achievements of high school students.</p>
          <p>Furthermore, the program is a key component of Measure #65 of the Implementation Plan for the National Cybersecurity Strategy (2022-2026) managed by the National Cybersecurity Agency (ACN).</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="cta-section">
        <a href="https://cyberchallenge.it" class="cta-button" target="_blank">Discover CyberChallenge.IT</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 120px 20px 60px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  }

  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .glitch {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    position: relative;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--accent-teal);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .text-block h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .text-block h2::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -5px;
    left: 0;
    width: 50px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent-gold);
  }

  .text-block p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .editions-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 30px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .edition-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  .edition-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .edition-card.accent {
    border-top: 3px solid var(--accent-green);
  }

  .edition-card:not(.accent) {
    border-top: 3px solid var(--accent-teal);
  }

  .cta-section {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 40px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-gold);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--accent-gold);
    color: var(--bg-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(237, 192, 30, 0.2);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .editions-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .hero-image {
      height: 250px;
    }

    .glitch {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 8vw, 2.5rem);
      word-break: break-word;
    }
    
    .text-block h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>
